 spelling of   Alice ."]},{"name":"Alis","meanings":["equivalent of <b>Alice</b> ."]}]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1705197,"age":50,"year":"1455","julianDay":2252488,"title":"Wars of the Roses","description":"Wars of the Roses was a series of English civil wars for control of the throne of England between the royal families House of Lancaster and the House of York. The name of the war was derived as the red rose was the symbol of the Lancastrians and the white rose was the symbol of the Yorks.","url":"https://www.history.com/topics/british-history/wars-of-the-roses","urlTitle":"History - Wars of the Roses","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"When Alice Pretyman was born in 1405, in Bacton, Suffolk, England, her father, William Pratyman, was 27 and her mother, Agnes Howlett, was 23. She married John Coke before 1419. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died on 10 May 1488, in her hometown, at the age of 83, and was buried in Bacton, Suffolk, England."},"et":{"1405–10 May 1488":"1405–10. mai 1488","1405–1488":"1405–1488","1407–1475":"1407–1475","1400–1440":"1400–1440","1400–1488":"1400–1488","1419–1461":"1419–1461","1427–Female":"1427–Surnud","1429–Male":"1429–Surnud","1378–1440":"1378–1440","1382–1456":"1382–1456","4 October 1440":"4. oktoober 1440","1440":"1440","1461":"1461","before 1419":"enne 1419","1382":"1382","1426":"1426","1403":"1403","1456":"1456","1455":"1455","1378":"1378","1400":"1400","1488":"1488","May 1488":"mai 1488","1475":"1475","Bef 1440":"enne 1440","10 May 1488":"10. mai 1488","1419":"1419","1429":"1429","1407":"1407","1405":"1405","1427":"1427","Bacton, Suffolk, England":"Bacton, Suffolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","East Ruston, Norfolk, England":"East Ruston, Norfolk, England","Dodington, Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, England"},"fi":{"1405–10 May 1488":"1405–10. toukokuuta 1488","1405–1488":"1405–1488","1407–1475":"1407–1475","1400–1440":"1400–1440","1400–1488":"1400–1488","1419–1461":"1419–1461","1427–Female":"1427–Kuollut","1429–Male